3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes an AI-based solution for image denoising. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper involves the use of neural networks for image denoising. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and denoising, which is a common task in multimedia applications.
